title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2010-2013 Chevrolet Camaro LED Tail Lights
description: This video provides specific directions for how to install Spyder Auto's LED tail lights in 2009-11 5th Generation Camaro models. Several styles of LED tail lights are available, however the method of installation is the same. This video showcase Spyder's Lamborghini Reventón/Aventador inspired LED tail lights.
